[[File:MicrosoftForefrontClientSecurity-ScreenCapture.png|thumb]]
'''Microsoft ForeFront'''是[[微軟|微軟]]的[[Microsoft_Windows|Microsoft Windows]]用戶端及伺服器端的一系列保安產品名稱，和[[Microsoft_Security_Essentials|Microsoft Security Essentials]]為姊妹軟件。

這一系列產品包括了以下各項產品：
* Microsoft Forefront Client Security（舊稱''Microsoft Client Protection''）
* Microsoft Forefront Security for [[Microsoft_Exchange_Server|Exchange Server]]（舊稱''Microsoft Antigen for Exchange''）
* Microsoft Forefront Security for [[Microsoft_Office_SharePoint_Portal_Server|SharePoint]]（舊稱''Antigen for SharePoint''）
* Microsoft Forefront Security for [[Microsoft_Office_Communications_Server|Microsoft Office Communications Server]]（舊稱''Antigen for Instant Messaging''）
* Microsoft [[Microsoft_Internet_Security_and_Acceleration_Server|Internet Security and Acceleration (ISA) Server 2006]]

